This paper discusses the use of utility functions in machine learning systems, which is a central topic in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also explores uncertainty in objectives, which is a common theme in machine learning and optimization (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), and computational complexity (cs.CC). Additionally, the paper discusses ethical considerations in AI systems, which is a topic in social and information sciences (cs.SI).
